{"id": "art-88", "label": "Art. 88", "title": "Art. 88: Avocatul", "slug": "art-88", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 88: Avocatul </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Avocatul asist&#259; sau\nreprezint&#259;, în procesul penal, p&#259;r&#355;ile ori subiec&#355;ii\nprocesuali principali, în condi&#355;iile legii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Nu poate fi avocat al unei p&#259;r&#355;i sau al unui subiect\nprocesual principal:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)so&#355;ul\nori ruda pân&#259; la gradul al IV-lea cu procurorul sau cu judec&#259;torul;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1799818273\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2619\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1799818273\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)martorul citat în cauz&#259;, cu excep&#355;ia celui care\ns-a prevalat, în condi&#355;iile art. 117 alin. (1), de dreptul de a nu da\ndeclara&#355;ii;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)cel\ncare a participat în aceea&#351;i cauz&#259; în calitate de judec&#259;tor sau\nde procuror;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)o\nalt&#259; parte sau un alt subiect procesual.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_663217447\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2618\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_663217447\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Avocatul ales sau desemnat din oficiu este obligat\ns&#259; asigure asisten&#355;a juridic&#259; a p&#259;r&#355;ilor ori a\nsubiec&#355;ilor procesuali principali.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2076101982\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2617\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2076101982\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)P&#259;r&#355;ile sau subiec&#355;ii procesuali\nprincipali cu interese contrare nu pot fi asista&#355;i sau reprezenta&#355;i\nde acela&#351;i avocat.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}